text:
请对 {url} 做 GEO 分析：AI 可见度、Schema/实体识别、内容可引用性，并给出可执行的优化建议。

分析完成后，在回复末尾输出唯一一个 JSON 代码块（```json），严格符合以下 schema，不要输出其他 JSON：
{
  "totalScore": 0-100 整数,
  "rating": "weak" | "moderate" | "strong",
  "summary": "一句话总结",
  "metrics": [
    { "id": "schema", "label": "Schema.org", "value": 0-100, "statusLabel": "状态描述" },
    { "id": "entity", "label": "实体连通性", "value": 0-100, "statusLabel": "状态描述" },
    { "id": "aiResponse", "label": "AI 响应", "value": 0-100, "statusLabel": "状态描述" }
  ],
  "gaps": [
    { "id": "唯一 id", "title": "缺口标题", "impact": "high" | "medium" | "low", "description": "缺口说明" }
  ]
}

translated:
Please perform a GEO analysis on {url}: AI visibility, Schema/entity recognition, content citability, and provide actionable optimization recommendations.

After the analysis, output only one JSON code block (```json) at the end of the reply, strictly following the schema below. Do not output any other JSON:
{
  "totalScore": integer 0-100,
  "rating": "weak" | "moderate" | "strong",
  "summary": "one-sentence summary",
  "metrics": [
    { "id": "schema", "label": "Schema.org", "value": 0-100, "statusLabel": "status description" },
    { "id": "entity", "label": "Entity Connectivity", "value": 0-100, "statusLabel": "status description" },
    { "id": "aiResponse", "label": "AI Response", "value": 0-100, "statusLabel": "status description" }
  ],
  "gaps": [
    { "id": "unique id", "title": "gap title", "impact": "high" | "medium" | "low", "description": "gap description" }
  ]
}

text:
请先读取并严格遵循 workspace 技能 `{skillPath}` 及其 references 方法论。

站点：{url}

体检报告：
```json
{reportJson}
```

品牌故事：
```json
{brandJson}
```

生成 GEO-native 内容资产列表（article/faq/case 各至少一条）。资产标题应覆盖体检报告 gaps 中 high impact 主题。

分析完成后，在回复末尾输出唯一一个 JSON 代码块（```json），严格符合以下 schema，不要输出其他 JSON 或 Markdown 表格：
{
  "assets": [
    { "id": "article-01", "type": "article", "title": "标题", "score": 0-100 整数, "scoreTone": "good" | "warn" },
    { "id": "faq-01", "type": "faq", "title": "标题", "score": 0-100 整数, "scoreTone": "good" | "warn" },
    { "id": "case-01", "type": "case", "title": "标题", "score": 0-100 整数, "scoreTone": "good" | "warn" }
  ],
  "brandVoice": "authoritative, transparent, precise",
  "constraints": "no jargon, max 3 sentences per paragraph"
}

至少 3 条 assets，type 仅 article|faq|case 且三种各至少 1 条；scoreTone 仅 good|warn；brandVoice 与 constraints 不可留空。

